{"word":"H6245 - עָשַׁת - ʻâshath - aw-shath' - Shine","slug":"H6245","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָשַׁת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻâshath"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-shath'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Shine"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05EA; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;shath</b> - <i>aw-shath'</i><p/>A primitive root; probably to be <i>sleek</i>, that is, <i>glossy</i>; hence (through the idea of <i>polishing</i>) to <i>excogitate</i> (as if <i>forming</i> in the mind): - shine, think."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1045\">H1045</a>, <a href=\"#/H6248\">H6248</a>, <a href=\"#/H6249\">H6249</a>, <a href=\"#/H6250\">H6250</a>, <a href=\"#/H6251\">H6251</a>, <a href=\"#/H6252\">H6252</a>, <a href=\"#/H6253\">H6253</a>, <a href=\"#/H6254\">H6254</a>, <a href=\"#/H6255\">H6255</a>"}]}